    <p class="w3-large">Welcome to Famous Fourth: A Tamaraw's Place, situated in the heart of Morayta near Far Eastern University. Beckoning students to step in and embrace the scent of freshly brewed coffee with eye-catching sweets to devour, our café is a cozy haven for students, teachers, or nearby people alike, looking for a place to catch up with friends and do their schoolwork while indulging in a freshly brewed coffee and a sweet treat. 
    <p class="w3-large w3-text-grey w3-hide-medium">At Famous Fourth, we take in our selection of famous sweet desserts  with a twist, perfectly crafted recipes  through time passed  down by generations, guaranteeing tempting glamour and taste. Indulge your cravings with smooth ensaymada and spanish bread that is hard to resist. Whether you're  taking a  break  from class  or  craving  a quick sip and bite, Famous  Fourth will be your go-to destination that can cater to all your needs, satisfying your stomach and  soul.</p>
